_description: External keyboard connection required
 Please connect or dock the external keyboard you want to use before
 proceeding

Template: asus-screen-toggle/usb_keyboard
Type: select
__choices: ${Choices}
_description: External keyboard for switching:
 Choose the external USB keyboard that will be used to trigger display
